litics of writing on the mechanical arts and the development of key Enlightenment concepts such as improvement, utility, and progress.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aArt and sciencezFrancexHistory. 0aEnlightenmentzFrance. 0aSciencexPhilosophy. 0aSciencezFrancexHistoryy18th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / France.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300231625?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300231625423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300231625/original  a978-3-11-063898-1  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles